# Local User Api

### 注册账号

POST {{$dotenv baseapi}}/local/user/register
Origin: {{$dotenv origin}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username":"{{$dotenv username}}",
    "password": "{{$dotenv password}}"
}

### 登录账号

POST {{$dotenv baseapi}}/local/user/login
Origin: {{$dotenv origin}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username":"{{$dotenv username}}",
    "password": "{{$dotenv password}}"
}

### 修改资料

PATCH {{$dotenv baseapi}}/local/user/info
Authorization: {{$dotenv authorization}}
Origin: {{$dotenv origin}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "description": "不可能！我的代码怎么可能会有bug！"
}

### 修改密码

PATCH {{$dotenv baseapi}}/local/user/password
Authorization: {{$dotenv authorization}}
Origin: {{$dotenv origin}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "oldPassword": "{{$dotenv password}}",
    "newPassword": "{{$dotenv password}}"
}
